name: Farm Animal Voyage: Tapped Out Adventure
name_original: Farm Animal Voyage: Tapped Out Adventure
description:
Farm Animal Voyage is the crazy chain reaction game that has already had millions and millions of levels played since it was introduced early this year. Come join the fun!

• Simple Objective: "Tap" all animals with a limited # of clicks
• Full Retina & iPhone 5 support!
• New PowerUps! will help you get through the hard levels!
• FREE Tips EVERY DAY!

Can you go all the way? Come join the fun
